--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
WHAT THIS MEANS FOR ODOO MODULES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

LGPL-3 is ideal for Odoo modules because:

1. ✅ You can use these modules in COMMERCIAL Odoo installations
2. ✅ You DON'T need to make your entire Odoo installation open source
3. ✅ You only need to share modifications to THESE specific modules
4. ✅ You can create proprietary modules that depend on these modules
5. ✅ Compatible with both Odoo Community Edition and Odoo Enterprise

IF YOU MODIFY THESE MODULES:
- You must keep this LICENSE file
- You must document your changes
- You must share the source code under LGPL-3 if you distribute

IF YOU ONLY USE THESE MODULES (without modification):
- You DON'T need to share your code
- You can use them freely in production
- You can have other proprietary modules

